    "body": "> Can I intercept certain key event to disable it?\r\n\r\nThere are some APIs to send and intercept keyboard/mouse events:\r\n\r\n* https://electron.atom.io/docs/api/web-contents/#event-before-input-event\r\n* https://electron.atom.io/docs/all/#winsetignoremouseeventsignore\r\n* https://electron.atom.io/docs/all/#contentssendinputeventevent\r\n\r\nYou can also extend Electron with C++ modules so it is feasible to add additional features to your app that access these platform APIs even if Electron does not currently expose it.\r\n\r\nClosing this out."
